law.text: Sixty percent (60%) of a fine imposed for the violation of this chapter or KRS Chapter 235 shall, when collected, be paid into the game and fish fund.
law.history: Amended 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 275, sec. 2, effective July 15, 1998. -- Amended 1976 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 17, sec. 45, effective January 1, 1978. -- Amended 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 200, sec. 23, effective June 19, 1952. -- Amended 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 68, sec. 16. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 1954d-25, 1954d-26.
